data.description: Welcome to your dream home the perfect location in a corner lot! This stunning 3-bedroom 2-bathroom and a den/office has been maintained and is ready for you to move in. This house has beautiful features:  tiles throughout the home, vaulted ceilings, kitchen with upgraded cabinets, granite countertop, stainless-steel appliances and renovated both bathrooms. The main bedroom has a huge space with breathtaking view of the inground pool. Has fruits trees like Mango, Avocado, Soursop, Coconut and more. Parking space for RV and Boat. This house won't last long.
